properties.name: Hwy12
properties.desc: Highway 12 near White Pass, trailhead parking both on north and south sides of the highway. White Pass is a small ski area 1/2 mile SW of the PCT on Hwy 12 with a motel [The Village Inn, whitepassvillageinn.com, 509-672-3131] and the Kracker Barrel convenience store [509-672-3105] with deli, laundry, and they accept hiker resupply packages. The town of Packwood is 20.5 miles W of the PCT on Hwy 12.

properties.name: KrackerBarrel
properties.desc: Kracker Barrel Store, 1/2 mile SW of PCT. Small store, deli, laundry, lodging nearby.

properties.name: SnoqualmiePass
properties.desc: Snoqualmie Pass is a busy interstate highway intersection and small ski area, on the PCT. They have the Summit Inn [thesummitinnsnoqualine.us, 425-434-6300, accepts packages for guests or for a fee], restaurants and a Chevron station [425-434-6688] with a market.
